cast.overview: New York, early 1960s. Against the backdrop of a vibrant music scene and tumultuous cultural upheaval, an enigmatic 19-year-old from Minnesota arrives in the West Village with his guitar and revolutionary talent, destined to change the course of American music.
cast.title: A Complete Unknown

details.biography: Lorin Angelica Doctor is an actor, writer, and producer residing in Los Angeles. She studied theatre at NYU Tisch and moved to Los Angeles to pursue a career in film. Whether it's film, theater, or television, she is inspired to make work that propels people to think outside of themselves and "get uncomfortable.".
details.name: Lorin Doctor
details.place_of_birth: New York City, New York, USA
